{"tid":705850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐時》：不再顧忌習總 侵侵有餘力懲罰中國","createTime":"2018-06-17T13:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T15:29:24.000Z","uid":55257,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00c817abca6e95a5cb1f462691554d8cddb94425","tid":705850,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"在美國公佈向價值500億美元（約3,900億港元）中國貨物徵收25%關稅後，中方隨即還擊，中美貿易戰不斷升溫。美國《紐約時報》刊登分析文章，美國總統特朗普早前礙於中國國家主席習近平，在北韓核問題談判中還有角色，暫時擱置貿易戰，但現在特金會已經舉行，中國難以阻礙美朝關係，特朗普已經有餘力去懲罰中國。<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》文章引述美國的戰略與國際研究中心（Center for Strategic and International Studies）的中國問題專家甘思德（Scott Kennedy），指目前中國不太可能在北韓問題上作出破壞，而白宮官員亦已達成共識，對中國施加某種處罰是合理的。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指出，特朗普曾經試圖透過談判，與北京達成一項能夠令美國企業進一步進入中國市場的協議，可是，這類談判沒有成果，因此特朗普不時使出狠招，同時也作出讓步，例如應習近平的要求，讓美國商務部「放生」中興通訊。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦認為他對中國出招，應該會有效，上周三（13日）他接受霍士新聞訪問時，稱中國「受不了他在貿易上的強力打擊」，而「未來兩周在貿易問題上，會更明確對中國採取強硬手段」，他更稱：「他們（中國）知道我們在做甚麼。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，中國官媒新華社發表評論文章，指摘美國挑起貿易戰，不但是失信於人，而且更是「輸了世界」，文章更批評美國「自身出毛病就找替罪羊，認為或為達目的不擇手段，絕不是解決問題的明智之舉」。"},{"pid":"2f9e7f2d0a0977158bbd35c7c2464ca903662893","tid":705850,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ac36c427671c5ac20b061536033eb596dd17fc","tid":705850,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95f68e18f7b69084bf7620d58ef2710796af6fa","tid":705850,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b6e7b3afb8e65ce0edcb6f49b758df4a73c52","tid":705850,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1ac36c427671c5ac20b061536033eb596dd17fc","tid":705850,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e07d5096a75b63a0c9d4f584e7dd01f8ab70bc","tid":705850,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bd6cef308070fe8b9f2898230f49061b12e9e4","tid":705850,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"中移動<br />\n中聯通<br />\n建行<br />\n工行<br />\n恒大<br />\n萬科<br />\n農行<br />\n交行<br />\n阿里<br />\n吉利<br />\n長城<br />\n中人壽<br />\n平保<br />\n騰訊<br />\n阿里<br />\n中石油<br />\n中海油<br />\n中石化<br />\n比亞迪<br />\n芧台<br />\n<br />\n隻隻靠國家壟斷, 大大隻, 美國無得入黎玩, 梗係唔滿意"},{"pid":"6336624c528f85b6bf98319abd85522be9207111","tid":705850,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942afb9cbd680b79562a147ea40249b868a0e86e","tid":705850,"uid":68285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人見到贏國改革開放就以為唔會行番計劃經濟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 查實贏國一直行緊計劃經濟操控所有商品價格"},{"pid":"2ca231b7615f00ed9a03098cd8193114c6b3b452","tid":705850,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"Trump只係一個過渡性人物"},{"pid":"33fabb80f8c5b3dd25ae1c33895606cd94c5a56e","tid":705850,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"又話China won<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853f4cee4429f44d532232ada844be2a93740d9b","tid":705850,"uid":12449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大傻瓜<img src=\"/